<li>Development of conical tonne buoy:
<ul>
<li>Solid plug at narrow end</li>
<li>Mooring ring attachment</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>By 1790: Nun buoy replaces older conical tonne:
<ul>
<li>Conical section below waterline</li>
<li>Barrel shape at waterline</li>
